I'll build this complete FishHunt Laravel application. This is a large project, so I'll implement it systematically with all the core features, models, migrations, controllers, policies, Blade templates, and the Hunt briefing system with demo mode.

<boltArtifact id="fishhunt-app" title="FishHunt - Laravel Fishing App">

<boltAction type="shell">
composer create-project laravel/laravel . --prefer-dist 2>&1 | tail -20
</boltAction>

<boltAction type="shell">
composer require laravel/breeze --dev 2>&1 | tail -5
</boltAction>

<boltAction type="shell">
php artisan breeze:install blade 2>&1 | tail -10
</boltAction>

